Fiat SpA Chief Executive Officer
Sergio Marchionne sees “more freedom” for alliances for Fiat
SpA after the spin-off of Fiat Industrial SpA, he said today in
Rome in a speech at the the annual meeting of the Italian
carmaker association  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
